A vast mechanical assembly line floating in a starry void, where glowing blue JAR containers travel along neon-lit conveyor belts, each jar containing miniature crystalline cityscapes representing frontend interfaces. Massive robotic arms with chrome and magenta accents carefully lower completed UI structures into open jars. In the background, towering server monoliths pulse with electric cyan energy, connected by streams of data visualized as flowing ribbons of light. The scene is bathed in deep purples, electric blues, and hot pink highlights, with holographic hexagonal patterns floating in the atmosphere. Rain falls gently, reflecting the neon glow off metallic surfaces. The perspective is dramatic, looking up at the machinery from below, emphasizing the industrial scale of the packaging process.
